": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 3", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": "Why do they use so many instanced rooms?"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "AWAY"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Doesn't it like... defeat the purpose of MMO?"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "SUSPICIOUS"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ..."}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "THINKING"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Sometimes I wonder about it myself. Wouldn't it be cheaper to use less instances?"}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "WONDERING"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Guess we'll never know."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "SHRUG"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 4", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " By the way, how did you like \\c[3]that jumping puzzle\\c[0] in Gaia's Garden?"}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Mon Dieu, the jumping ones are bad already."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "EXHAUSTED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Ones where you have to hit switches on time are even worse."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "CURIOUS"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Or when you have to escort a slowly traveling VRP."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "TOWARDS"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ...!"}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "EXHAUSTED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": "They always reminded me of escort quests in other RPGs. Never liked them."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "LAUGH"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Me neither."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "EXHAUSTED"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 5", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Most enemies in CrossWorlds are kind of cool."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Hate the flying ones though."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "EMBARRASSED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Jap. They keep getting away if you get too close."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "LAUGH"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Most of the time, it turns the fight into a waiting game."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "SKEPTICAL"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " It's always some dumb papagun for me."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "EXHAUSTED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " He stays up high and keeps throwing stupid bananas."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "MOPING"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " They are actually melons, but I know that feeling all too well."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "LAUGH"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " At least Lea can take care of them with her ranged attacks."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "WATCH_OUT_BADASS"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ..."}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "WHISTLING"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 6", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " How is your job, Lukas?"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "AWAY"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Project scope increased, but deadlines are left unchanged."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "SKEPTICAL"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Meanwhile, most of the department has no clue what they are doing."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " You know, business as usual."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "LAUGH"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Oui, some things never change."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "EXHAUSTED"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 7", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " I wonder if Lea will also get a job."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "CURIOUS"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " How?"}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "SURPRISED_AWAY"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " I'm sure Instatainment will find something for you to do."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "WONDERING"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ..."}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "THINKING"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 8", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Just got an idea."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Lea may perform play-testing of new content."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "WINK"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Like an early access?"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "CURIOUS"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ...!"}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "EXCITED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Knowing Instatainment, it's gonna be one hell of a \\c[3]Long Early Access\\c[0]."}, "person": {"person": "main.schneider", "expression": "WINK"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", 